STATE
v.
Edward WILLIAMS, III. No. 318P15-1. Supreme Court of North Carolina. Sept. 24, 2015. Edward Williams, III, Marion, for Williams, Edward (III). Kimberly N. Callahan, Assistant Attorney General, for State of North Carolina. Gary W. Frank, District Attorney, for State of North Carolina.

Opinion

The following order has been entered on the motion filed on the 8th of September 2015 by Defendant to Appoint Counsel:

"Motion Dismissed as moot by order of the Court in conference, this the 24th of September 2015."
